{"tid":1778300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港共連手足在澳洲都唔放過 求政府庇護","createTime":"2019-12-10T23:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T01:48:17.000Z","uid":139698,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe00768443003dca1d6c224db8afef874a03f02","tid":1778300,"uid":139698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T23:56:20.000Z","msg":"澳洲報 The Guardian 報導<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong democracy protester says he was ambushed by masked Chinese men in Australia<br />\n<br />\n一位&ldquo;前線&rdquo;香港民主抗議者最近因擔心自己的安全而逃離了香港，他說，他在澳大利亞城市遭到一群蒙面中國人的伏擊和追捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足幫手推， 拒絕赤化 全球覺醒 圍剿共匪<br />\n<br />\n盡快推動及通過馬茨尼法案（澳洲版香港人權法案）制裁有關打壓在港人權的官員及警察，進一步向其施壓，為人權、自由、公義表明立場。<br />\n<br />\nSign it<br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/6tvMJdRhNf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2F6tvMJdRhNf&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=2edd7c38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/6tvMJdRhNf</a><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SSCHUeH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSSCHUeH.jpg&h=2253cc34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource, <br />\n<a href=\"https://amp.theguardian.com/australia-news/2019/dec/10/hong-kong-democracy-protester-says-he-was-ambushed-by-masked-chinese-men-in-australia?__twitter_impression=true&amp;fbclid=IwAR33Y8AbtOni3j1v0UVSetDn2PissusirgP2-f5KN20_qrQgn_YSypL1K1o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.theguardian.com%2Faustralia-news%2F2019%2Fdec%2F10%2Fhong-kong-democracy-protester-says-he-was-ambushed-by-masked-chinese-men-in-australia%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue%26fbclid%3DIwAR33Y8AbtOni3j1v0UVSetDn2PissusirgP2-f5KN20_qrQgn_YSypL1K1o&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=e3e36852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://amp.theguardian.com/australia-news/2019/dec/10/hong-kong-democracy-protester-says-he-was-ambushed-by-masked-chine